    "The 'Collaboration and Community' category, referenced by 15 experts (38.5%), underscores the value placed on collective efforts and community-driven initiatives.",
    "'Openness' was highlighted by 14 experts (35.9%), emphasizing the need for opensource data and accessible research practices.",
    "The category 'Decentralization,' mentioned by 10 experts (25.6%), reflects the commitment to decentralized and autonomous approaches.",
    "Lastly, 'Incentives and Rewards,' cited by nine experts (23.2%), point to the importance of recognizing and rewarding contributions within the DeSci ecosystem.",
    "For the formation of each category regarding the guiding principles of DeSci, quotes from the experts participating in the survey were used, as shown in Table 15."
